<BaseLayout title = "We need you!" sideBarActiveItemID="join us">
  
    <div class="flex text-3xl w-full font-bold mb-5 justify-left">We need you!🫵🏾</div>
  <div class="py-2">
<article class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
<ol class="list-decimal">
  Join us and help us run this thing.
  
<ul>  You can sign up to volunteer for: </ul>

    <ul>    -  Investigative Journalism: You will be talking to a lot of people, gathering information, experiences, and accounts (in any language), and then articulate and consolidate them into articles.</ul>

    <ul>    -  Reporting/Interviewing: You will be reporting on the events occurring on campus, such as club events, protests, etc.</ul>

    <ul>    -  Creative Content Writing (in English and Indian languages): You will be helping in writing and structuring special articles, giving ideas for various sections and helping in refining the ideas of the other teams.</ul>

    <ul>    -  Language Editing: You would be checking and refining the language of the entire content of the magazine. </ul>

    <ul>    -  Videography and Video Editing: You would be required to help shoot and edit videos for Kalpa's YouTube channel and make reels for its Instagram page.</ul>

    <ul>    -  Designs and Illustrations: You will plan the page layouts and illustrate the articles.</ul>

    <ul>    -  Website Management: This department is in charge of handling Kalpa’s website. They will also be responsible for maintaining and updating it when necessary.</ul>

    <ul>    -  Publicity: This domain entails online and offline publicity for Kalpa. Offline publicity consists of putting up posters on campus, and online publicity involves managing Kalpa’s social media accounts.</ul>


<ul>Drop us a mail at kalpa@sac.iiserpune.ac.in</ul>

</article>

</BaseLayout>